{"ts":"2026-07-06T08:03:10.608Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/453\n\n## Problem\n`pm plan materialize --json` returns materialized[] entries with only `id`; title/type/parent are undefined in the response projection (data on disk is correct). Callers need a pm get round trip per created item to confirm.\n\n## Proposed fix\nInclude { id, title, type, parent, tags } per materialized entry — same compact projection list rows use.\n\n## Definition of done\nmaterialize --json response carries the confirmation fields; spec updated; no extra reads needed to verify materialization."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-ypha"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-453: plan materialize --json response omits title/type/parent on materialized entries"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-453: materialize response projection returns only id per created item though disk data is complete. Duplicate check: searched materialize projection — no existing item."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":3},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","bug","gh-issue","plan"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:10.608Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:10.608Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":45},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"materialize --json materialized[] entries include id/title/type/parent/tags; spec updated; no extra get round-trip needed for confirmation"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value"